 the more likely the behavior will occur.<br>2-","time":1490332175,"resto":118038330,"id":"1eBnkYPx","country":"US","country_name":"United States"},{"no":118044844,"now":"03\/24\/17(Fri)01:10:50","name":"Anonymous","com":"<a href=\"#p118044718\" class=\"quotelink\">&gt;&gt;118044718<\/a><br>Task Two: Rating the Susceptibility<br>2-75. Once susceptibility has been assessed, a rating is determined. This rating aids in prioritizing TAs for<br>PSYOP, as well as determining a recommended PSYOP COA to achieve the SPO. Susceptibility is rated<br>on a 1 to 5 scale:<br>\u2022 5 = Very susceptible (high-to-moderate reward, low risk, and consistent with values and<br>beliefs).<br>\u2022 4 = Susceptible (high-to-moderate reward, moderate-to-low risk, mostly consistent with values<br>and beliefs).<br>\u2022 3 = Moderately susceptible (moderate-to-low reward, moderate-to-low risk, somewhat consistent<br>with values and beliefs).<br>\u2022 2 = Slightly susceptible (low reward, moderate-to-low risk, somewhat consistent with values<br>and beliefs).<br>\u2022 1 = Not susceptible (low reward, moderate-to-high risk, not consistent with values and beliefs).","time":1490332250,"resto":118038330,"id":"1eBnkYPx","country":"US","country_name":"United States"},{"no":118044898,"now":"03\/24\/17(Fri)01:11:13","name":"Anonymous","com":"<a href=\"#p118044492\" class=\"quotelink\">&gt;&gt;118044492<\/a><br>my friend, the one who got his teeth fucked up, talked to his mother about it and they&#039;re looking to press charges on the two nigs that were beating on him, who are the main nigs that keep fucking with me and leading groups.","time":1490332273,"resto":118038330,"id":"mXa6Lcse","country":"US","country_name":"United States"},{"no":118044953,"now":"03\/24\/17(Fri)01:11:43","name":"Anonymous","com":"<a href=\"#p118044844\" class=\"quotelink\">&gt;&gt;118044844<\/a><br>Task Three: Making a Recommendation<br>2-76. Based upon the assessment of susceptibility, a recommendation is given. This recom